{"title":"西藏萨迦格言","authors":["王尧选"],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":11,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"西藏萨迦格言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对赞扬和夸张不表示喜悦；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对辱骂讥刺不表示气愤；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全心全意追求学问；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这才是真正的学者的风度。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有德行的人会遇到暂时的困难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们不必为他们担忧；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮有时会被天狗吃了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一刹那工夫自然会解脱的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王尧选译"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}